#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/visualize_data/charts.rst:50
msgid ""
"For a chart inserted from an Odoo graph view, click :guilabel:`Data` on the "
"menu bar then select the relevant chart, as prefaced by the :icon:`fa-bar-"
"chart` :guilabel:`(chart)` icon, e.g., :icon:`fa-bar-chart` *(#1) Sales "
